1499 English Surely we cannot offer the Tibetan population attention only when it suits us ? 
1500 English In sum , Madam President , I would urge you to ensure that a real dialogue is established according to the Dalai Lama' - s five - point peace plan ; it will then be a happy day for Tibet' - s entire population . 
